title: Thanks, Scientists!
description:
On Earth Day, April 22, citizens of America and the whole world will celebrate both the planet we live on and the people who study how it works. Scientists often devote their entire lives to learning more about how the world is put together and how we can get the most out of being here.

Today we salute four unique people who, after decades of hard work in the laboratory, left behind incredible legacies that help our families be healthier and happier every day.

WATCH THE VIDEO ON OUR SITE: http://ow.ly/9TVN30b1k2p
